An Xfire plugin for Pidgin

Gfire features:

    * Friend's list
    * Add & Remove friends
    * View friend's current game (games list updated weekly)
    * View friend's profiles
    * Join friend's server
    * Detects games and logs game time
    * Set your status as "Away from Keyboard (AFK)"
    * Set custom status

NOTE: Each user who wishes to use this plugin needs to copy
/usr/doc/gfire-0.7.1/gfire_games.xml to ~/.purple

